{"title":"数据结构代码实现：栈","uid":"6b2186d2c0aed026593e0e9c03232d97","slug":"DataStructure-SqStack","date":"2020-05-11T09:45:27.000Z","updated":"2020-05-19T14:18:40.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DataStructure-SqStack.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200511174712.png","content":"<h2 id=\"栈的定义\"><a href=\"#栈的定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"栈的定义\"></a>栈的定义</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#define MaxSize 50\n#define ElemType int\ntypedef struct &#123;\n    ElemType data[MaxSize];\n    int top;\n&#125;SqStack;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"初始化栈\"><a href=\"#初始化栈\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"初始化栈\"></a>初始化栈</h2><ul>\n<li>top=-1代表为空栈<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">void InitStack(SqStack &amp;S)&#123;\n    S.top&#x3D;-1;&#x2F;&#x2F;top&#x3D;-1代表为空栈\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"判断栈空\"><a href=\"#判断栈空\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"判断栈空\"></a>判断栈空</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">bool StackEmpty(SqStack &amp;S)&#123;\n    return S.top &#x3D;&#x3D; -1;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"入栈操作\"><a href=\"#入栈操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"入栈操作\"></a>入栈操作</h2><ul>\n<li>判断是否栈满</li>\n<li>非空，则将栈顶指针加一再入栈<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">bool Push(SqStack &amp;S,ElemType e)&#123;\n    if(S.top&#x3D;&#x3D;MaxSize-1)&#x2F;&#x2F;判断是否栈满\n    &#123;\n        return false;\n    &#125;\n    S.data[++S.top]&#x3D;e;&#x2F;&#x2F;栈顶指针加一再入栈\n    return true;\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"出栈操作\"><a href=\"#出栈操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"出栈操作\"></a>出栈操作</h2><ul>\n<li>判断是否为空栈</li>\n<li>非空,则记录出栈的元素,栈顶指针减一<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">bool Pop(SqStack &amp;S,ElemType &amp;e)&#123;\n    if(S.top&#x3D;&#x3D;-1)&#x2F;&#x2F;判断是否为空栈\n    &#123;\n        return false;\n    &#125;\n    e&#x3D;S.data[S.top--];&#x2F;&#x2F;记录出栈的元素\n    return true;\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"读取栈顶元素\"><a href=\"#读取栈顶元素\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"读取栈顶元素\"></a>读取栈顶元素</h2><ul>\n<li>判断是否为空栈</li>\n<li>非空,则直接读取栈顶元素<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">bool GetTop(SqStack S,ElemType &amp;e)&#123;\n    if(S.top&#x3D;&#x3D;-1)&#x2F;&#x2F;判断是否为空栈\n    &#123;\n        return false;\n    &#125;\n    e&#x3D;S.data[S.top];&#x2F;&#x2F;记录栈顶元素\n    return true;\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n","text":"栈的定义#define MaxSize 50 #define ElemType int typedef struct &#123; ElemType data[MaxSize]; int top; &#125;SqStack; 初始化栈 top=-1代表为空栈void InitS...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/categories/数据结构.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"},{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":11,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"考研","slug":"考研","count":11,"path":"api/tags/考研.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A0%88%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">栈的定义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96%E6%A0%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">初始化栈</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E6%A0%88%E7%A9%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">判断栈空</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%A5%E6%A0%88%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">入栈操作</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%87%BA%E6%A0%88%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">出栈操作</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AF%